This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and part-of-speech tagging. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it discusses the use of deep learning and neural approaches. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DL (Deep Learning) as it specifically mentions the use of neural networks.
